  "title": "Danik vs Ai'kani",
  "summary": "Grand Admiral Danik Kreldin holds the defector Sandor Woden hostage in the Moff's office on Selene, taunting him that the Jedi Ai'kani has walked into a trap by coming to rescue him. Ai'kani arrives, surrenders her lightsaber to the Imperial escort, and confronts Danik, who, fueled by dark-side rage, lunges at her with his Corellian Rapier. Ai'kani rolls clear, seizes his backup sword, and the two duel, the Padawan handicapped by the heavy unfamiliar blade and drawing first blood against herself before landing a winding blow that drops the aging Danik. When reinforcements burst in with her confiscated saber, Ai'kani recovers the weapon, cuts down the troopers, and frees Sandor, while Danik, beaten and humiliated, flees to his shuttle. Battered and bleeding, Ai'kani and Sandor fight their way to a turbolift and escape by cutting through a window onto a stolen transport, as Danik retreats to the Malevolence to report his failure and plot his revenge.",
